      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STIFF LUCK (1) hit the ground running off the inside draw and there until late when holding on for a minor finishing second (20.09) at this track in a Grade 5 over 366m. Rates highly and will give a great sight. HARA'S JACKSON (5) stalked the lead from a low draw then burst clear to score (25.34) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5 over 457m. Expected to feature again. LESTER BANNER (3) goes very well this trip starting eight times for three wins and three minors. Placed last time (20.32) at this track in a Restricted WIN, finishing third and beaten 2 lengths. Looks one of the chances. ZIPPING NARWHAL (2) is worth consideration after filling a hole from the same draw last start.",
